      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"people won't miss you\" part... that's kind of what I mean. It feels less like a break and more like the truth. I look at my contact list and I don't see people, I just see names in a directory. If I just... disappeared, the work would still get done, the tickets would still be closed. It's like I'm already gone, just a ghost in the machine. It wouldn't even be a disruption, just a tiny bit of silence where a cursor used to be.",
